nd numerous other mausoleums and madrasas also bear witness to the great history of Samarkand. \nIf you want to see as much of Samarkand as possible, you should set off with your tour guide straight after breakfast. The best way to get around the city is by bus or on foot. \nLunch and dinner not included. \nOvernight stay in a bed and breakfast guesthouse in twin rooms. \nMeals: Breakfast at hotel\n	\N
